It's really important.

00:15:47.412 --> 00:15:50.315
It's valuable for us here also.

00:15:50.315 --> 00:15:53.252
So, that day, that was
a special day that day.

00:15:53.252 --> 00:15:55.954
I'll tell you, I did
amazing discovery.

00:15:55.954 --> 00:15:58.556
I was exhausted, as usual.

00:15:58.556 --> 00:16:02.928
And starving, because I've
been starving quite a lot.

00:16:02.928 --> 00:16:05.264
And, that was a laundry day.

00:16:06.565 --> 00:16:09.301
I wash a bit my
stuff on the way.

00:16:10.435 --> 00:16:13.405 align:start size:84% position:16%
So I had my long, it's
like a long shirt,

00:16:13.405 --> 00:16:16.675
long sleeve, and
I took some water,

00:16:16.675 --> 00:16:20.311
and I decide to wash
it, so I squeeze it,

00:16:20.311 --> 00:16:21.713
and I decide to have a nice, ah,

00:16:21.713 --> 00:16:25.650
to get rid of that
water a little bit.

00:16:25.650 --> 00:16:28.620
And suddenly I hear a noise.

00:16:28.620 --> 00:16:31.456
It be like, (high
pitched bird call?)

