Like a crinky noise like that.

00:16:33.057 --> 00:16:35.294
I was like, what?!

00:16:35.294 --> 00:16:38.663
And suddenly I'm just
like, under the bushes

00:16:38.663 --> 00:16:41.299
straight away, looking
for what's going on.

