Is just, do not do this.

00:16:48.040 --> 00:16:51.076
You have to be on the
ground, all the time.

00:16:51.076 --> 00:16:54.679 align:start size:94% position:6%
And then, I'm there,
waiting to see that bird,

00:16:54.679 --> 00:16:57.116 align:start size:97% position:3%
because I know all of the
birds, I know all the plants,

00:16:57.116 --> 00:17:01.252 align:start size:97% position:3%
I've been studying that
landscape for days and years.

00:17:01.252 --> 00:17:03.455
Never heard about that bird.

00:17:03.455 --> 00:17:05.190
Anyway, I forgot
about that thing,

00:17:05.190 --> 00:17:08.393
took my jacket, and
smashed it again.

