And I know they have to
drink two times a day.

00:19:04.977 --> 00:19:07.712 align:start size:84% position:16%
So I know there would
be water around.

00:19:07.712 --> 00:19:09.814
Or if I find a type of plant,

00:19:09.814 --> 00:19:12.784
I would know exactly what
kind of roots I can find,

00:19:12.784 --> 00:19:14.453
and I can find food.

00:19:15.887 --> 00:19:18.123
My food, it's all I've got.

00:19:19.758 --> 00:19:22.828 align:start size:84% position:16%
You know, you realize
after you peel,

00:19:23.729 --> 00:19:25.797
life, it's like an onion.

00:19:26.698 --> 00:19:28.800
You peel the onion.

00:19:28.800 --> 00:19:32.036 align:start size:84% position:16%
Once you peel where
you come from,

00:19:32.036 --> 00:19:34.372
who you are in this society,

